" /></blockquote><br />\n想知interest 同discount received係有咩 用番上面例子"},{"pid":"fb101a61c6f51018128fdfcaea6afab7810770d7","tid":169743,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"連問問題都未識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858570dacdc1ee98f8f865901c876e454fd46a59","tid":169743,"uid":46320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>dse中五程度都唔識好難幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有咩specific既問題要問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利伸:acct maj<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想知interest 同discount received係有咩 用番上面例子</blockquote><br />\n條問題無咪assume 0囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係間間公司都有同一set revenue/expense架嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb535fecd98ae887e6aa4e46971afbabf8ef86a","tid":169743,"uid":4008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打識做未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我睇下d notes仲係唔係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申ive考過淨係溫呢題同少少短答都B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我求知不得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想知interest 同discount received係有咩 用番上面例子</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://subject.jccssyl.edu.hk/subjects/commerce/subhtml/ych/會考會計練習/筆記-會計的基礎介紹.doc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsubject.jccssyl.edu.hk%2Fsubjects%2Fcommerce%2Fsubhtml%2Fych%2F%E6%9C%83%E8%80%83%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E7%B7%B4%E7%BF%92%2F%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98-%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9.doc&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=13bb96f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://subject.jccssyl.edu.hk/subjects/commerce/subhtml/ych/會考會計練習/筆記-會計的基礎介紹.doc</a><br />\n<br />\n你可以睇下d名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要分到A,L,C,R,E 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf7e723a6984c12a64696e81f40b525653a26da","tid":169743,"uid":32636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:38:56.000Z","msg":"Other income簡單黎講姐係除左sale之外既收入 但係點分邊個係income呢<br />\n你用普通logic就得 <br />\n例如購貨折扣<br />\n你可以諗下你買野 人地比discount你 你係賺左定蝕左<br />\n<br />\n利申 有幫人補開dse acct 希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce21e84bad53dc6483b195b273c5b87516eac78","tid":169743,"uid":32636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打識做未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我睇下d notes仲係唔係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申ive考過淨係溫呢題同少少短答都B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我求知不得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想知interest 同discount received係有咩 用番上面例子</blockquote><br />\n唔會話有咩架wo<br />\n但係有個陣你一定睇得出"},{"pid":"0fd0883c963ee09c79ee710b9d021ae92706d306","tid":169743,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打識做未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我睇下d notes仲係唔係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申ive考過淨係溫呢題同少少短答都B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我求知不得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想知interest 同discount received係有咩 用番上面例子</blockquote><br />\n唔會話有咩架wo<br />\n但係有個陣你一定睇得出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最重要係個原則<br />\n<br />\nSales同cost就係同你個主業有關，other incone即係不務正業<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，你本身開鋪賣波鞋嘅，咁賣鞋收入咪revenue，買鞋成本就係cost，你錢多攞左去放數收返黎d利息就係other income<br />\n<br />\n調返轉，你本身係放數嘅，你收嘅利息咪係revenue，你個債仔無錢還俾左對波鞋你，你買鬼左佢，咁嗰夠錢咪other income囉"},{"pid":"487681a164f2cd9c6f63236535eed0812d3cf082","tid":169743,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:05:39.000Z","msg":"呢條連DSE都難過佢喎清"}]}